Herbal preparations made by water maceration of the rhizome (root) of
Neorautanenia mitis (A. Rich) Verdc. (Fabacae)
are used by Traditional Medicine (TM) practitioners and livestock owners in Nigeria , as an effective means of treating the symptoms of diarrhea in both humans and livestock (
